    <blockquote>
      <p>"The research on autistic adults in the workforce consistently shows the same thing: it's not the work that's the problem — it's the environment. When we get the environment right, autistic employees are among the most focused, loyal, and precision-oriented colleagues in any organization. The investment in getting it right is almost always worth it."</p>
      <cite>— Dr. Kyle Daigle, Neurotherapist & Co-founder, Neurosage Hub</cite>
    </blockquote>

